The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation
		 Sunday, August 25, 2002 				 Burial probe
																								Madurai, Aug. 24 (PTI): An inquiry has been ordered into the Peraiyur temple ceremony in which children were buried alive for some seconds as part of a vow, official sources said.																								The probe follows instructions from the National Human Rights Commission and the state government. 
